data.description: Adorable fully fenced home on a cul-de-sac in a great neighborhood.  Right near the Carol Stream paths that connect so much of the town and to schools and parks like Papoose Tot lot. Top notch schools. Green areas everywhere including next to 881 Niagara. Lot's of "NEWS" like a new roof in 2022, furnace and air conditioner, water heater, and all new appliances.  It really is move in ready and waiting for you!   "AS-IS" but buyer will be provided a 13 month Home Warranty!
